- 'solid following base' means having more than 500 followers;
- 'impressive impact' indicates an influence score > 0.8;
- 'top influencers' suggests selecting the top 10 results based on influence score.

sql:
SELECT AVG(tweets_count) as average_tweets
FROM (
  SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) as tweets_count
  FROM tweets
  GROUP BY user_id
) as user_tweets;

SELECT user_name
FROM users
WHERE followers_count = (SELECT MAX(followers_count) FROM users);

